    "question": "Problem 11.10. Consider a family of stationary observers in a stationary spacetime, i.e. their 4-velocity is proportional to the time Killing vector $\\pmb{\\xi}$ . Each observer arranges his spatial basis vectors so that they connect to the same neighboring observers for all time $t$ , where $\\pmb{\\xi} = \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}$.\\n(1) Show that $\\mathcal{L}_{\\pmb{\\xi}} \\mathbf{e}_{\\widehat{\\alpha}} = 0$ , where $\\mathbf{e}_{\\alpha}$ is a basis vector of the stationary observer.",
